title: Evi11
description: Devil Evi, who was born in the weakest, most inferior eleventh caste of hell, was prepared for a boring monotonous life - draining cauldrons after boiling people in oil. But Evi does not care about fate and the laws of hell, as he deserves deeds worthy of Satan. Controls: Arrow keys - movement Space - jump Z - shoot C - jab with a pitchfork Enter - select items in the menu Esc - exit to the menu Features: Beautiful graphics. Game for a bad, but somehow nice character. A variety of gameplay. Two modes of complexity (auxiliary blocks at a easy level). https://s16.postimg.org/alo3ij479/image.jpg https://s9.postimg.org/64ostgizz/image.jpg
